Valueformoney
23 May 2017 By Flipkart Customer On flipkart.com

Good laptop, good brand good configuration at good price. 7 years back I bought Inspiron 1545 compared to that build quality plastic is bad. Touch pad getting tuk tuk plastic sound. Don't know about durability but performance is good from last 2 days. Uninstalling Ubuntu and keeping windows 7 is like hell. If you have genuine windows it may be easy. Graphics softwares not installed, getting error. Getting battery for 2-3 hours.

Good
02 Jun 2018 By Shravan kumar Ponnoju On flipkart.com

Review after 10 days of use: I received this Dell laptop with all features mentioned in the description.But it has CD/DVD drive which is not mentioned. It comes with pre installed windows 10 home edition and office 365.you need to activate office within the time period using Microsoft account.it has i5 8th Gen,8gb ddr4 ram,2gb ddr5 dedicated Radeon graphics. Processor speed is 1.60GHZ 1.80GHZ. fingerprint sensor is good.Display is not good while playing videos,and viewing angles also bad. Speakers average.processor speed looks like slow but handles multiple tasks easily.McAfee comes with 458 days subscription.webcam is not hd. Battery backup in normal browsing around 5 hours. overall ratings out of 5 processor : 4 Display : 2.5 Graphics : 4 Design : 4 Battery : 4.5
